    <text>
        <body>
        	<div1 type="letter">
        		<head>Jim to Mademoiselle Marcelle Guerin, Sunday.  n.d.</head>
        		
        		<opener>
            <dateline>Sunday</dateline>
            
            <salute>Dear Marcelle:</salute>
        		</opener>
        		
            <p>
            I do want
            to see you so much.
            and I was going over
            Sat. night but Mrs. Weeks
            told me you had company.
            I’m sorry to have missed
            you when you came to 
            call on Mrs. Weeks.
            </p><p>
            I thank you
            for your nice note.  I do
            
            <pb n="[p.2]"/>
            
            hope you’ll get the
            leave you speak of 
            when Mlle. Du B &mdash; returns.
            </p><p>
            I was getting on
            much better, but to day,
            after not being able to
            sleep during the night,
            I am only able to move
            with two canes.  Queer
            sort of trouble, &mdash; I can’t
            figure it out.  It goes
                        
            <pb n="[p.3]"/>
            
            and then comes again.
            </p><p>
            Pavelka writing from 
            Luxeuil says that Prince
            entered with lower wing
            shot away and one of
            the masts cut.  Must
            be exaggerated, for with
            all that wrong a machine
            wouldn’t keep the air.
            There isn’t much doing.
            Only six machines, and the
            
            <pb n="[p.4]"/>
            
            other pilots sit around
            and do nothing.
            </p><p>
            I hope you’re not
            overworking.  I shall drop
            in for an evening call
            just as soon as possible.
            </p>
        		
        		<closer>
            <salute>Best to you</salute>
            
            <signed>Jim</signed>
        		</closer>
        		
            
            <!-- [With this letter is an envelope addressed to Mademoiselle Marcelle Guerin, 148 Bis Rue de Longchamp, E.V.] -->
            
            </div1>
        </body>
